  <text x="20" y="28" fill="#fafafa" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="16" font-weight="700">ITEP Report vs. the PARITY Act at a Glance</text>
  <text x="20" y="48" fill="#a1a1aa" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="13">Per the report and bill text (as of July 18)</text>
  <rect x="16" y="68" width="158" height="300" rx="10" fill="#18181b" stroke="#3f3f46"/>
